```{=latex}
\begin{theorem}[Functional Equation]
```
The functional equation in the case of curves: `
\begin{align*}  
\zeta_X(q^{-1} t^{-1} ) = \pm q^{2-2g \over 2} t^{2-2g} \zeta_X(t)
.\end{align*}`{=tex}

```{=latex}
