We'll prove this in a special case: if $X$ is quasicompact and
separated, Čech cohomology computes derived functor cohomology.

::: {.claim title="1"}
```{=latex}
\begin{claim}[1]
```
Every cover can be refined to a *finite* cover by affines, using
quasicompactness.

```{=latex}
